        <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/">CC-BY-SA</a>.
      </li>
      <li>The
        <a href="https://github.com/awmottaz/tonymottaz.com">code for this site</a>
        is
        <a href="https://github.com/awmottaz/tonymottaz.com/blob/main/LICENSE.txt">BSD-3-Clause</a>.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <ul class="link-list _no-bullets">
      <li><a href="https://fosstodon.org/@tonymottaz">Mastodon: @tonymottaz@fosstodon.org</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tony-mottaz/">LinkedIn</a></li>
    </ul>
  </footer>
</body>

</html>